.TH JTUTIL-MIRROR "1" "April 2026" "jtutil-mirror manual" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
jtutil-mirror \- Find mirrored data in a ROM file
.SH DESCRIPTION
If a ROM file contains the same data in more than one address
position, the size of the ROM can be reduced.
jtutil mirror tries to find address bits which are not needed to address
the whole content of the ROM.
.SS "Usage:"
.IP
jtutil mirror [flags]
.SS "Flags:"
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
help for mirror
